Document: CSGCylinder3D
Path: godot/classes/class_csgcylinder3d.rst
Summary: Properties and member variables of the CSGCylinder3D class, including cone shape, height, material, radius, polygon count, and surface smoothing settings.

- cone (bool): Enables cone shape instead of cylinder. Default: false
- height (float): Vertical dimension of the cylinder. Default: 2.0
- material (Material): Surface material applied to the shape
- radius (float): Horizontal radius of the cylinder. Default: 0.5
- sides (int): Number of polygonal segments around the circumference. Default: 8
- smooth_faces (bool): Enables smooth shading for faces. Default: true